noria:TroubleTicket_TT002 noria:troubleTicketPartyIntervention org:OrganizationalUnit_DBA .
noria:TroubleTicket_TT003 noria:troubleTicketPartyIntervention org:OrganizationalUnit_SecurityTeam .

noria:TroubleTicketNote_TT001_Note2 noria:troubleTicketNoteCorrelatedExecution pep:CorrectiveMaintenanceAction_FiberCheck .
noria:TroubleTicketNote_TT002_Note1 noria:troubleTicketNoteCorrelatedExecution pep:ChangeAction_DBIndexOptimize .
